{
  "stem": "17001.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 177.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, you should see how much bread she was throwing through the fence to this Czech man.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, so they are stealing from us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, so if one or two people won't have bread they have inside, they could give it to them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You crazy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could never do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I made up my mind from then on if I want to steal or if I want to do something, I do it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't need any judgment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the judgment, I don't go too far.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then I went, and I had seen after [GERMAN] one day that there were these people we-- you know, as shortage as you have and hardship as you have, there is still a class different.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You are the Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They call it the stupid [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then is the one who are coming from the car path area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They are the one who are the most resourceful because they were going through hardship before the [GERMAN], and they had to survive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they had no income.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The matter of fact, there were times while we were home that we heard that they went to the rabbi and they asked the rabbi, being that we don't have wheat to make matzohs, can we eat corn?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rabbi said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's how bad it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what happened in Auschwitz, there was also a class different.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These people, they'd be called the [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were like rats.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When the [HUNGARIAN] was coming from the kitchen, they would ran over-- because some of their friends were carrying the [HUNGARIAN]-- and they dig into it, and they ran away.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the meantime, the one who was carrying it helped them.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
